  {
    "hotel_id": "7413757",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/st-signature-chinatown/hotel/singapore-sg.html",
    "name": "ST Signature Chinatown",
    "detail": "I stayed in this hostel for two days, small cabin and medium cabin, both with windows. The room size is quite reasonable that enable to fully open a 27 inch luggage. I love the adjustable air con. Shower rooms and toilets are clean and with very nice ventilation. The 2200W Philips hair dryer are superb for girls! I have not stayed in a hostel with such nice hair dryer before! The location is very convenient. For cheaper choice of food, you may either go to the Chinatown food street opposite or Maxwell hawker Centre with few mins walk. Or simply go to the Restaurants & Bars right behind the hostel. If the hostel can add a lugguage slideway on the stairs / add more hooks or shelf inside the shower rooms for placing clothes, that would be definitely excellent. Will consider to stay again if choosing a hostel in Singapore next time.",
